WEBVTT

01:51.875 --> 01:54.417
PREVIOUSLY ON "DEXTER"...

01:54.417 --> 01:57.125
Man: TWO TREASURE HUNTERS MADE
A GHASTLY DISCOVERY TODAY

01:57.125 --> 01:59.000
WHEN THEY STUMBLED
ON WHAT APPEARS TO BE

01:59.000 --> 02:00.250
AN UNDERWATER GRAVEYARD

02:00.250 --> 02:02.125
IN A CREVICE
OFF THE COAST OF MIAMI.

02:02.125 --> 02:04.667
AGENT LUNDY HAS REQUESTED
THE FOLLOWING OFFICERS

02:04.667 --> 02:06.291
FOR HIS JOINT TASK FORCE.

02:06.291 --> 02:09.917
WE'RE A TEAM, AND OUR FIRST PLAY
IS I.D.ing THOSE BODIES.

02:09.917 --> 02:11.667
I'M DEXTER MORGAN.

02:11.667 --> 02:12.792
I KNOW WHO YOU ARE.

02:12.792 --> 02:14.542
HOPING THEY'LL TALK TO YOU?

02:14.542 --> 02:16.000
THEY ALWAYS SPEAK.

02:16.000 --> 02:18.542
YOU JUST GOT TO ASK
THE RIGHT QUESTION.

02:18.542 --> 02:20.375
Dexter:
HARRY WAS RIGHT.

02:20.375 --> 02:24.041
NOTHING STAYS BURIED,
PERHAPS NOT EVEN ME.

02:24.041 --> 02:25.792
Capt. Astor: SHOULD I BE WORRIED
ABOUT PASCAL?

02:25.792 --> 02:27.417
AND YOU'RE ASKING ME
BECAUSE?

02:27.417 --> 02:29.291
BECAUSE YOU'VE DONE
THE JOB.

02:29.291 --> 02:31.166
SO, IF SHE'S OUT,
THAT MEANS YOU'RE BACK IN.

02:31.166 --> 02:34.875
I WON'T DIGNIFY RUMORS, CAPTAIN.
PASCAL'S FINE.

02:34.875 --> 02:36.500
Gabriel: YOU NEED TO, UH,
WRAP YOUR WRISTS

02:36.500 --> 02:38.291
SO YOU DON'T HURT
YOURSELF AGAIN.

02:41.625 --> 02:44.083
I'M SORRY.

02:44.083 --> 02:46.125
WE'LL GET YOU
INTO A PROGRAM,

02:46.125 --> 02:48.458
WE'LL GET YOU THE HELP
YOU NEED,

02:48.458 --> 02:50.291
AND I WILL BE THERE
FOR YOU.

02:50.291 --> 02:54.333
I'M DEXTER,
AND I'M NOT SURE WHAT I AM.

02:54.333 --> 02:57.875
EVERYONE IN THAT ROOM HAS HEARD
OR LIVED FAR WORSE

02:57.875 --> 02:59.333
THAN ANYTHING
YOU'VE EVER DONE.

02:59.333 --> 03:02.000
I DOUBT IT.

03:02.000 --> 03:03.750
HOW FULL OF SHIT ARE YOU?

03:03.750 --> 03:05.500
THE MASK IS SLIPPING.

03:05.500 --> 03:09.250
PEOPLE WHO NEVER MATTERED BEFORE
ARE SUDDENLY STARTING TO MATTER.

03:09.250 --> 03:11.125
DIDN'T YOUR TOUR
IN THE ARMY

03:11.125 --> 03:13.500
INCLUDE SOME SPECIAL OP
IN HAITI?

03:14.750 --> 03:16.792
THERE'S MY SPONSOR.
REALLY, WHERE?

03:32.959 --> 03:36.792
JUST AS THE WORST HEAT WAVE
IN YEARS HITS MIAMI,

03:36.792 --> 03:38.917
THE HEAT IS ALSO ON ME.

03:38.917 --> 03:40.333
IT'S WEEK THREE

03:40.333 --> 03:42.458
OF THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER
INVESTIGATION,

03:42.458 --> 03:44.208
AND SUPERDUPER
SPECIAL AGENT LUNDY

03:44.208 --> 03:46.500
HAS YET TO THROW UP
HIS HANDS AND SAY,

03:46.500 --> 03:49.875
"WOW, THIS GUY'S GOOD.
I GIVE UP."

03:49.875 --> 03:51.875
DEXTER, PLEASE.

03:51.875 --> 03:52.917
DO YOU WANT ME TO HELP?

03:52.917 --> 03:54.667
NO, I JUST --
I JUST NEED YOU TO MOVE.

03:54.667 --> 03:56.375
AH.

03:56.375 --> 04:00.041
I'M SORRY. IT'S JUST, YOU KNOW,
MY MOTHER'S COMING TODAY.

04:00.041 --> 04:01.458
I CERTAINLY DO.

04:01.458 --> 04:03.458
I HAVEN'T SEEN HER
IN SO LONG,

04:03.458 --> 04:05.917
AND I JUST WANT EVERYTHING
TO BE NICE.

04:05.917 --> 04:07.875
WE KIND OF ENDED THINGS
ON BAD TERMS.

04:07.875 --> 04:10.583
SHE AND PAUL DIDN'T GET ALONG
SO WELL.

04:10.583 --> 04:12.875
A LOT OF PEOPLE AND PAUL
DIDN'T GET ALONG SO WELL.

04:12.875 --> 04:14.083
[ Sighing ] YEAH.

04:14.083 --> 04:18.041
BUT I -- I THINK SHE'S WILLING
TO PUT THAT BEHIND US.

04:18.041 --> 04:19.792
SHE HEARD
ABOUT PAUL'S PASSING,

04:19.792 --> 04:21.959
AND SHE WANTED TO COME
AND BE SUPPORTIVE.

04:21.959 --> 04:23.750
THAT SOUNDS PROMISING,
RIGHT?

04:23.750 --> 04:25.875
ABSOLUTELY.

04:25.875 --> 04:27.417
[ SIGHS ]

04:27.417 --> 04:31.083
YOU'LL LIKE HER, DEXTER.
SHE'S GREAT.

04:31.083 --> 04:33.166
SHE'S A VERY STRONG WOMAN.

04:33.166 --> 04:34.500
I'LL KEEP THAT IN MIND

04:34.500 --> 04:37.000
IN CASE I HAVE ANY
HEAVY LIFTING TO DO.

04:37.000 --> 04:38.583
IT'S TOO HOT.

04:38.583 --> 04:41.375
I KNOW, HONEY.
HOPEFULLY IT'LL COOL DOWN SOON.

04:41.375 --> 04:43.333
DID YOU SLEEP ANY BETTER
LAST NIGHT?

04:43.333 --> 04:44.542
MORE NIGHTMARES?

04:44.542 --> 04:46.917
WHAT WAS IT, THE BIG,
SCARY GHOST OR THE ALLIGATOR?

04:46.917 --> 04:49.375
NO, THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

04:50.875 --> 04:51.917
OH, HONEY.

04:51.917 --> 04:53.959
HE WOULD NEVER HURT YOU.

04:53.959 --> 04:57.959
BUT I'LL LET YOU IN
ON A SECRET.

04:57.959 --> 04:59.667
MY SISTER, DEBRA,

04:59.667 --> 05:02.000
WHO IS A SECRET POLICE AGENT
NINJA WARRIOR,

05:02.000 --> 05:03.792
SAID HE ONLY KILLS
BAD PEOPLE,

05:03.792 --> 05:05.792
AND YOU'RE NOT A BAD PERSON,
ARE YOU?

05:05.792 --> 05:07.000
NO.

05:07.000 --> 05:08.500
THEN YOU'RE QUITE SAFE.

05:08.500 --> 05:10.458
WHY DON'T YOU GO GET DRESSED,

05:10.458 --> 05:12.959
AND I WILL MAKE YOU
SOME BREAKFAST, OKAY?

05:14.458 --> 05:15.959
[ GROANS ]

05:15.959 --> 05:17.291
IT MAKES ME SO ANGRY

05:17.291 --> 05:21.709
THAT THERE'S SOME MONSTER
OUT THERE SCARING MY SON.

05:21.709 --> 05:23.709
I GOT TO GO TO WORK.

05:23.709 --> 05:25.792
YOU KNOW,
I HOPE THEY CATCH HIM TODAY.

05:25.792 --> 05:28.792
AND I'M NOT A VIOLENT PERSON,
BUT I HOPE THEY HURT HIM.

05:28.792 --> 05:30.959
HAVE A GOOD DAY.

05:30.959 --> 05:33.333
MAKE UP YOUR MIND.

05:43.125 --> 05:44.917
IN OUR MOST PARANOID MOMENTS,

05:44.917 --> 05:47.792
WE FEAR THAT EVERYONE
IS TALKING ABOUT US.

05:47.792 --> 05:49.375
THAT'S BECOME MY REALITY.

05:51.000 --> 05:53.500
I CAN'T HEAR
WHAT THEY'RE SAYING,
BUT I KNOW IT'S NOT NICE.

05:53.500 --> 05:55.667
Lundy: ALL RIGHT,
LET'S GET STARTED.

05:55.667 --> 05:59.000
WE HAVE POSITIVE I.D.s ON ALL 18
OF OUR COMPLETE BODIES.

05:59.000 --> 06:01.959
13 OF THOSE HAVE FELONY RECORDS.

06:01.959 --> 06:03.709
ORGANIZED CRIME.

06:03.709 --> 06:06.208
NOPE. NO CONNECTION
TO ORGANIZED CRIME,

06:06.208 --> 06:07.583
NO MUTUAL GANG
AFFILIATION, EITHER.

06:07.583 --> 06:10.834
BUT ALL 13 WERE EITHER TRIED
FOR MURDER

06:10.834 --> 06:13.166
OR AT LEAST SUSPECTED OF MURDER.

06:13.166 --> 06:14.709
STILL,
YOU HAVE YOUR PATTERN.

06:14.709 --> 06:16.583
YES, WE JUST DON'T KNOW
WHAT IT MEANS.

06:20.500 --> 06:23.041
I THINK WE GO OUT
WITH THIS NEWS IMMEDIATELY.

06:23.041 --> 06:25.000
WHAT NEWS IS THAT?

06:25.000 --> 06:26.959
THE NEWS THAT
OUR SERIAL KILLER

06:26.959 --> 06:28.542
IS ONLY KILLING THE DREGS
OF SOCIETY,

06:28.542 --> 06:31.959
THAT GOOD, MORAL PEOPLE
HAVE NOTHING TO FEAR.

06:31.959 --> 06:34.250
BUT, CAPTAIN, THAT'S ALL --
UH...

06:34.250 --> 06:36.333
THIS IS THE ONLY LEAD
WE HAVE.

06:36.333 --> 06:38.500
WE NEED TO KEEP IT
TIGHTLY WRAPPED.

06:38.500 --> 06:40.375
LAST NIGHT,
AN ELDERLY MAN SHOT HIS SON

06:40.375 --> 06:41.583
WHEN HE CAME HOME LATE,

06:41.583 --> 06:43.709
THOUGHT IT WAS
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER.

06:43.709 --> 06:46.208
WE'VE GOT A CITY
IN CHAOS HERE, FRANK.

06:46.208 --> 06:48.709
I UNDERSTAND YOU WANTING
TO REASSURE THE PEOPLE.

06:48.709 --> 06:50.333
GOOD.
THEN WE'RE IN AGREEMENT.

06:56.250 --> 06:59.542
DEX, I GOT THIS HUGE BREAK
IN THE BAY HARBOR CASE.

06:59.542 --> 07:00.875
BULLSHIT.

07:00.875 --> 07:03.000
I MEAN, REALLY?

07:03.000 --> 07:05.166
GUYS, GUYS.

07:05.166 --> 07:07.083
YOU ARE NOT GOING TO...

07:07.083 --> 07:10.959
I REFUSE TO BELIEVE
THAT VINCE MASUKA IS THE MAN

07:10.959 --> 07:12.917
WHO SINGLE-HANDEDLY
BRINGS ME DOWN.

07:12.917 --> 07:17.083
I ALSO KNOW DENIAL IS THE FIRST
STAGE OF THE GRIEVING PROCESS

07:17.083 --> 07:20.041
FOR THOSE WHO LEARN
THEY'RE GOING TO DIE.

07:23.875 --> 07:26.250
I NEED TO FIND OUT
WHAT MASUKA KNOWS,

07:26.250 --> 07:30.959
BUT I'VE GOT TO BE CALM
AND CENTERED...

07:30.959 --> 07:33.125
AND FOCUSED.

07:33.125 --> 07:36.083
TIME FOR A VISIT TO MY SPONSOR.

07:36.083 --> 07:38.417
I NEED HELP.

07:48.875 --> 07:50.834
[ CRACKLING ]

07:57.750 --> 07:59.125
HI!

07:59.125 --> 08:01.458
HEY! JUST A MINUTE!

08:04.792 --> 08:05.959
DEXTER.

08:05.959 --> 08:07.375
HOPE I'M NOT INTERRUPTING
ANYTHING.

08:07.375 --> 08:10.333
NO.
GLAD YOU CALLED.

08:10.333 --> 08:11.667
[ GROANS ]

08:11.667 --> 08:13.625
JUST GIVE ME A MINUTE.

08:13.625 --> 08:16.125
YEAH, HAVE A LOOK AROUND.

08:26.041 --> 08:30.333
SO, HEY, I WAS GONNA GO AND GET
SOME ART SUPPLIES.

08:30.333 --> 08:33.125
IS THAT ALL RIGHT?
DO YOU WANT TO COME?

08:33.125 --> 08:35.375
YEAH, I'M JUST
ON MY LUNCH BREAK.

08:35.375 --> 08:37.333
EXCELLENT.

08:37.333 --> 08:39.583
WHY ARE THEY EATING
EACH OTHER?

08:39.583 --> 08:42.542
DON'T KNOW. ASK THEM.

08:46.500 --> 08:49.417
♪ IT'S A LONG WAY HOME ♪

08:49.417 --> 08:52.125
♪ AND IT'S ALL I SEE
IS DARKNESS ♪

08:52.125 --> 08:55.208
♪ IT'S A LONG WAY HOME ♪

08:55.208 --> 08:57.583
DO YOU LIKE THE HEAT?

08:57.583 --> 09:01.500
UM...NOT REALLY.
I'M PARTIAL TO AIR-CONDITIONING.

09:01.500 --> 09:03.208
I LOVE IT.

09:03.208 --> 09:05.875
IT MAKES ME FEEL LIKE
THE WHOLE WORLD COULD EXPLODE

09:05.875 --> 09:07.208
AT ANY MOMENT.

09:07.208 --> 09:09.166
THAT'S A PLEASANT THOUGHT.

09:09.166 --> 09:11.667
IS THERE AN ART STORE
NEAR HERE?

09:11.667 --> 09:13.083
SO, YOU BEEN USING?

09:13.083 --> 09:14.834
USING WHAT? OH.

09:14.834 --> 09:16.458
UH, NO.

09:16.458 --> 09:19.208
NO DRUGS.
PERFECTLY CLEAN.

09:19.208 --> 09:20.375
LOOK WHAT WE HAVE HERE!

09:22.291 --> 09:24.083
JESUS.
WHAT ARE YOU --

09:24.083 --> 09:25.000
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

09:27.041 --> 09:28.750
COME ON.

09:33.500 --> 09:36.667
ARE YOU GONNA HELP OR WHAT?

09:41.166 --> 09:44.125
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

09:44.125 --> 09:45.709
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

09:49.834 --> 09:52.583
THAT WAS A LITTLE WEIRD.

09:52.583 --> 09:56.291
SO, IF YOU'RE PERFECTLY CLEAN,
WHY'D YOU CALL?

09:56.291 --> 10:01.000
I-I'M UNDER A LOT OF PRESSURE
AT WORK.

10:01.000 --> 10:04.208
I WAS HOPING YOU COULD MAYBE
GIVE ME SOME QUICK TIPS

10:04.208 --> 10:06.250
ON HOW TO DEAL
WITH THE URGES.

10:06.250 --> 10:08.917
THERE ARE NO QUICK TIPS.

10:08.917 --> 10:11.542
OH. I SEE.

10:20.583 --> 10:21.834
[ BELL RINGS ]

10:21.834 --> 10:24.417
SOMEONE'S GONNA HEAR THAT.
THEY'LL THINK
IT'S THE WIND.

10:24.417 --> 10:26.625
I THOUGHT WE WERE GOING
TO GET ART SUPPLIES.

10:26.625 --> 10:31.250
THAT'S EXACTLY
WHAT WE'RE DOING.

10:31.250 --> 10:34.458
I WORK WITH FOUND ART.

10:34.458 --> 10:36.750
IT'S MORE LIKE STOLEN ART.

10:36.750 --> 10:39.709
IS THIS WHAT A SPONSOR NORMALLY
DOES ON THEIR FIRST MEETING?

10:39.709 --> 10:41.125
I DON'T KNOW.

10:41.125 --> 10:43.125
I'VE NEVER SPONSORED
ANYONE BEFORE.

10:43.125 --> 10:44.333
REALLY?

10:44.333 --> 10:45.542
YEAH, BUT DON'T WORRY.

10:45.542 --> 10:47.750
I'VE HAD ALL  KINDS
OF SPONSORS.

10:47.750 --> 10:49.709
LEARNT FROM THE BEST.

10:49.709 --> 10:52.208
YOU DO REALIZE I WORK
WITH THE POLICE DEPARTMENT?

10:52.208 --> 10:55.750
IF WE GET CAUGHT,
YOU CAN FLASH YOUR BADGE.

10:55.750 --> 10:59.625
I DON'T HAVE A BADGE.
I HAVE A LAMINATE.

11:03.625 --> 11:06.500
COULD WE TALK
ABOUT WHY I CALLED YOU?

11:06.500 --> 11:08.625
YEAH, SURE.

11:08.625 --> 11:11.166
UM [CLEARS THROAT]
YOU WANT HELP.

11:12.291 --> 11:14.041
SO, TELL ME.

11:17.250 --> 11:18.667
WHY DO YOU USE?

11:21.041 --> 11:23.875
WHY?

11:23.875 --> 11:26.291
I DON'T KNOW.
IT'S JUST PART OF WHO I AM.

11:28.125 --> 11:29.959
AND WHO ARE YOU?

11:32.000 --> 11:33.542
I'M A...

11:35.333 --> 11:37.166
...BAD PERSON.

11:37.166 --> 11:38.750
[ LAUGHS ]

11:38.750 --> 11:42.417
YOU HAVEN'T GOT THE FIRST IDEA
WHO YOU ARE, HAVE YOU?

11:42.417 --> 11:45.792
DEXTER, MEET DEXTER.

11:45.792 --> 11:49.792
I'M GONNA HELP THE TWO OF YOU
GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER.

11:51.667 --> 11:54.000
THAT DOESN'T REALLY SEEM
NECESSARY.

11:54.000 --> 11:56.875
THE FIRST STEP TO RECOVERY
IS ACCEPTING WHO YOU ARE.

11:56.875 --> 12:00.250
I THOUGHT THE FIRST STEP WAS
ADMITTING YOU HAVE A PROBLEM.

12:00.250 --> 12:02.291
AND BEFORE YOU CAN ACCEPT
WHO YOU ARE,

12:02.291 --> 12:03.750
YOU HAVE TO KNOW
WHO YOU ARE.

12:03.750 --> 12:06.041
SO THAT'S OUR FIRST JOB.

12:06.041 --> 12:09.875
YOU'RE GOING TO TELL ME ALL
YOUR DEEPEST, DARKEST SECRETS.

12:12.792 --> 12:16.125
Woman: THERE IS SOMETHING OFF
ABOUT HIM, HARRY.

12:16.125 --> 12:18.959
YOU KNOW WHY.

12:18.959 --> 12:20.875
ALL RIGHT, LOOK.

12:20.875 --> 12:24.166
IT WOULDN'T HURT TO HAVE HIM
TESTED, WOULD IT?

12:26.166 --> 12:28.250
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

12:31.291 --> 12:34.041
HELLO? YES.

12:34.041 --> 12:35.834
IT -- JUST A SEC.

12:35.834 --> 12:38.667
I GOT TO GET BACK.
DEAD BODY.

12:38.667 --> 12:41.458
HMM. HOW MANY TIMES HAVE YOU
USED THAT  ONE BEFORE?

12:41.458 --> 12:43.750
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

12:43.750 --> 12:48.375
SO, THE HUSBAND'S NAME
IS BARNES, B-A-R-N-E-S.

12:48.375 --> 12:51.208
WHAT DO WE HAVE?

12:51.208 --> 12:52.834
HELLO, DEXTER.

12:52.834 --> 12:56.291
UH, GUNSHOT VICTIM,
ALISHA BARNES, 36.

13:00.250 --> 13:01.834
SO, I HEARD THERE MAY BE
SOME BIG BREAK

13:01.834 --> 13:03.208
IN THE BAY HARBOR
BUTCHER CASE.

13:03.208 --> 13:04.917
UH, COULD BE.

13:04.917 --> 13:06.834
THE NEIGHBOR HEARD
THE VICTIM

13:06.834 --> 13:09.417
ARGUING WITH HER HUSBAND
LAST NIGHT, CURTIS BARNES.

13:09.417 --> 13:10.875
MASUKA WAS PRETTY EXCITED
ABOUT IT.

13:10.875 --> 13:12.542
HUSBAND'S CAR IS GONE.

13:12.542 --> 13:14.625
NOBODY KNOWS WHERE HE IS.
ANY IDEA WHAT THEY FOUND?

13:14.625 --> 13:18.375
CAN WE CONCENTRATE
ON THIS CASE HERE, PLEASE?

13:18.375 --> 13:20.792
SURE.

13:20.792 --> 13:23.458
THE KILLER WAS STANDING
RIGHT ABOUT WHERE YOU ARE,

13:23.458 --> 13:25.542
SERGEANT DOAKES.

13:25.542 --> 13:27.792
TWO SHOTS TO THE CHEST.

13:27.792 --> 13:29.625
I ONLY SEE ONE HOLE
IN THE CHEST.

13:29.625 --> 13:31.291
YEAH, THEY ARE
THAT CLOSE TOGETHER.

13:31.291 --> 13:32.625
IT'S VERY IMPRESSIVE SHOOTING.

13:32.625 --> 13:36.834
IT LOOKS LIKE THE BULLETS TOOK
NEARLY IDENTICAL EXIT PATHS,

13:36.834 --> 13:38.333
JUDGING FROM THE SPRAY.

13:38.333 --> 13:40.625
AND THIS WAS ALL TOPPED OFF
BY A FINAL SHOT TO THE HEAD.

13:40.625 --> 13:43.083
SHE WAS MOZAMBIQUED.

13:43.083 --> 13:44.417
LaGuerta: WHAT?

13:44.417 --> 13:46.917
TRIPLE-TAPPED.

13:51.291 --> 13:52.458
OH, SHIT.

13:52.458 --> 13:55.959
I'M GUESSING
THIS IS CURTIS BARNES.

13:55.959 --> 13:58.709
HERE HE IS IN WHAT LOOKS LIKE
SOMALIA, AFGHANISTAN,

13:58.709 --> 14:00.500
A RUSSIAN GRENADE,
A KURDISH DAGGER,

14:00.500 --> 14:03.291
AND TELL ME THAT SHIT WASN'T
STOLEN FROM SADDAM'S PALACE.

14:03.291 --> 14:04.625
WHAT ARE YOU SAYING?

14:04.625 --> 14:07.458
I'M SAYING
ASSHOLE'S SPECIAL OPS.

14:07.458 --> 14:09.000
THERE'S NO DOUBT ABOUT IT.

14:09.000 --> 14:10.166
HUH, THEY'RE GENERALLY KNOWN

14:10.166 --> 14:11.792
FOR SETTLING THEIR ARGUMENTS
SO PEACEABLY.

14:11.792 --> 14:14.458
DON'T GET SMUG WITH ME.

14:15.792 --> 14:18.083
SOUNDS LIKE WE'RE
IN YOUR WORLD, JAMES.

14:18.083 --> 14:20.834
YEAH, I'LL TAKE LEAD
ON THIS ONE.

14:29.500 --> 14:31.709
Lundy:
PICK A BODY.

14:31.709 --> 14:32.542
SIR?

14:32.542 --> 14:34.959
I WANT YOU EACH TO PICK A BODY.

14:34.959 --> 14:37.375
THIS IS WHERE THE CASE
IS GOING TO BE MADE.

14:37.375 --> 14:39.875
WE HAVE 13 SUSPECTED MURDERERS,

14:39.875 --> 14:44.041
AND THEN WE HAVE
THESE  GENTLEMEN.

14:44.041 --> 14:48.041
ROBERT THATCHER,
JANITOR FOR THE SCHOOL DISTRICT

14:48.041 --> 14:49.792
WITH NO CRIMINAL RECORD.

14:49.792 --> 14:51.458
MARCUS WHITE,

14:51.458 --> 14:53.542
TOW-TRUCK DRIVER,

14:53.542 --> 14:56.291
NO CRIMINAL RECORD.

14:56.291 --> 14:59.041
AND THIS -- THIS IS...

14:59.041 --> 15:02.375
OSCAR SOTA.

15:05.000 --> 15:06.875
WHAT'S HIS STORY?

15:06.875 --> 15:09.875
NAVAL ENGINEER
FOR THE PORT OF MIAMI,

15:09.875 --> 15:11.583
MEMBER OF
THE STEWARDSHIP COUNCIL

15:11.583 --> 15:13.417
OF ST. TARSICIA CATHOLIC CHURCH,

15:13.417 --> 15:16.083
MARRIED, LOVED, RESPECTED.

15:16.083 --> 15:19.458
BUT HE WAS FOUND IN A BAG
UNDER THE SEA WITH 13 KILLERS.

15:19.458 --> 15:21.000
WHY?

15:21.000 --> 15:23.500
ANSWER THAT QUESTION,
THEN WE REALLY KNOW SOMETHING.

15:23.500 --> 15:26.083
I...I GOT HIM.

15:26.083 --> 15:27.709
OSCAR SOTA.

15:29.917 --> 15:32.834
WHY DID THE KILLER CUT THEM UP
LIKE THIS?

15:32.834 --> 15:34.333
EASE OF DISPOSAL.

15:34.333 --> 15:35.083
OR FOR FUN.

15:38.041 --> 15:40.875
YOU DON'T KILL THIS MANY PEOPLE
BECAUSE IT'S A CHORE.

15:40.875 --> 15:42.875
YOU DO IT
'CAUSE YOU LIKE IT.

15:44.250 --> 15:47.000
OKAY.

15:47.000 --> 15:48.083
GREAT.

15:49.500 --> 15:52.291
TOMORROW.
THE BARNES CASE?

15:52.291 --> 15:54.792
YEAH, THAT WAS A BUDDY OF MINE
FROM SPECIAL OPS.

15:54.792 --> 15:56.834
HE HEARD CURTIS BARNES
WAS STILL IN MIAMI.

15:56.834 --> 15:58.083
OH.

15:58.083 --> 16:00.375
THE ONLY PART OF THAT
THAT I FIND SURPRISING

16:00.375 --> 16:01.542
IS THAT YOU HAVE A BUDDY.

16:02.625 --> 16:05.917
IT TURNS OUT BARNES AND I
BOTH WERE RANGER RRD.

16:05.917 --> 16:08.083
REGIMENTAL RECONNAISSANCE
DETACHMENT,

16:08.083 --> 16:10.250
THE GUYS YOU'RE NOT SUPPOSED
TO KNOW ABOUT

16:10.250 --> 16:12.041
WHO GET IN
BEFORE EVERYBODY ELSE.

16:12.041 --> 16:13.792
A BROTHER IN ARMS.

16:13.792 --> 16:15.250
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

16:15.250 --> 16:17.959
MY BUDDY PUT ME IN TOUCH
WITH A GUY FROM CURTIS' UNIT.

16:17.959 --> 16:19.417
HE'S WILLING TO TALK TO ME.

16:19.417 --> 16:20.625
GOOD.

16:20.625 --> 16:21.875
I GOT YOUR BLOOD REPORT.

16:21.875 --> 16:23.750
IT'S ALL PRETTY
STRAIGHTFORWARD.

16:23.750 --> 16:25.291
I'D BE CAREFUL, THOUGH.

16:25.291 --> 16:27.166
WHY IS THAT?

16:27.166 --> 16:28.959
THE TRAJECTORY OF THE BULLETS
ARE ALL LEVEL,

16:28.959 --> 16:30.375
EXACT SAME ANGLE OF ORIGIN.

16:30.375 --> 16:32.750
I'D SAY ALL THREE SHOTS WERE
FIRED IN LESS THAN A SECOND.

16:32.750 --> 16:34.917
IT'S VERY IMPRESSIVE SHOOTING.

16:37.333 --> 16:39.083
MORGAN.

16:46.125 --> 16:48.542
I'M GONNA NEED YOU TO RUN
SOME TESTS ON THIS SHIRT.

16:48.542 --> 16:50.166
IS THERE BLOOD?

16:50.166 --> 16:51.166
NO BLOOD.

16:51.166 --> 16:53.083
I'M REALLY THE BLOOD GUY.

16:53.083 --> 16:56.959
IT'S A SMELL.
IT SMELLS LIKE A WOMAN.

16:58.375 --> 16:59.500
WHICH PART?

17:01.417 --> 17:03.333
WHO CAN IDENTIFY THIS
FOR ME?

17:03.333 --> 17:06.083
UH...

17:06.083 --> 17:09.709
YOU KNOW, THAT'S REALLY
MASUKA'S AREA.

17:09.709 --> 17:11.000
HE'S DEFINITELY YOUR MAN.

17:14.333 --> 17:15.792
THANKS.

17:21.917 --> 17:25.208
ANYTHING I CAN DO TO OVERBURDEN
MASUKA IS TO MY ADVANTAGE.

17:25.208 --> 17:27.917
TRUST ME, I'M NOT ABOVE
SENDING PIZZAS AND HOOKERS

17:27.917 --> 17:30.166
TO HIS HOUSE
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE NIGHT.

17:38.917 --> 17:41.166
WELL, EVERYTHING'S UNPACKED.

17:41.166 --> 17:45.333
THE BACK BEDROOM'S SMALL,
BUT IT'S QUIETER.

17:45.333 --> 17:47.709
I'M JUST HAPPY TO BE HERE,
THAT'S ALL.

17:47.709 --> 17:48.917
YOU'RE ALWAYS WELCOME.

17:48.917 --> 17:50.583
AM I?

17:50.583 --> 17:51.667
I WASN'T SURE.

17:51.667 --> 17:53.166
OF COURSE YOU ARE.

17:55.333 --> 17:58.709
ALL THESE YEARS
WITHOUT AN INVITATION.

17:58.709 --> 18:00.875
I JUST -- I THOUGHT
YOU DIDN'T WANT TO COME.

18:00.875 --> 18:02.792
I MEAN, YOU AND PAUL --
OH, NONSENSE.

18:02.792 --> 18:04.542
I WASN'T GONNA LET THAT
KEEP ME AWAY

18:04.542 --> 18:07.041
FROM MY DAUGHTER
AND MY  GRANDCHILDREN.

18:07.041 --> 18:10.917
BUT YOU DID LET IT
KEEP YOU AWAY.

18:10.917 --> 18:12.917
LET'S NOT ASSIGN
BLAME, RITA.

18:12.917 --> 18:15.542
NOTHING GOOD EVER
COMES OF THAT.

18:15.542 --> 18:18.250
WE'LL JUST HAVE TO MAKE UP
FOR LOST TIME, THAT'S ALL.

18:20.417 --> 18:22.375
HI.
HEY.

18:25.458 --> 18:27.834
DEXTER,
THIS IS MY MOTHER.

18:27.834 --> 18:30.667
GAIL.
SO NICE TO MEET YOU.

18:30.667 --> 18:32.125
NICE TO MEET YOU, TOO,
DEXTER.

18:36.583 --> 18:41.583
I'VE ALWAYS BEEN GOOD
WITH PARENTS.

18:41.583 --> 18:44.333
THE KEY IS TO SIMPLY THINK
OF THEM AS ALIENS

18:44.333 --> 18:46.875
FROM A DISTANT UNIVERSE.

18:48.834 --> 18:53.166
"YOU HAVE FIBERS AND THREADS
UNKNOWN TO US.

18:55.083 --> 18:57.250
YOUR ANCIENT CUSTOMS
INTRIGUE ME."

18:59.709 --> 19:04.208
SO, DEXTER, TELL ME EVERYTHING
THERE IS TO KNOW ABOUT YOU.

19:04.208 --> 19:08.417
"YOU HAVE MADE ME YOUR
SWORN ENEMY, EVIL WOMAN."

19:08.417 --> 19:10.834
I WORK IN
THE FORENSICS DEPARTMENT

19:10.834 --> 19:12.458
FOR THE MIAMI METRO P.D.,

19:12.458 --> 19:14.583
AND I'M VERY FOND
OF YOUR DAUGHTER.

19:16.083 --> 19:18.458
GOOD ANSWER. I'M ALSO VERY FOND
OF MY DAUGHTER.

19:18.458 --> 19:20.375
YOU DID A GOOD JOB
RAISING HER.

19:20.375 --> 19:22.083
30 YEARS AS A SCHOOLTEACHER.

19:22.083 --> 19:24.291
I'VE GOT A LITTLE EXPERIENCE
WITH CHILDREN,

19:24.291 --> 19:26.917
AND I SEE A YOUNG MAN
WHO IS NOT EATING.

19:26.917 --> 19:28.542
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

19:28.542 --> 19:30.750
HE'S SCARED THE BUTCHER'S
GONNA GET HIM.

19:30.750 --> 19:34.166
OH, WELL, REMEMBER,
HE ONLY GETS BAD PEOPLE.

19:34.166 --> 19:37.834
I WAS BAD TODAY.
I THREW A BALL AT TOMMY ALVAREZ.

19:37.834 --> 19:41.000
WELL, THAT'S NOT TOO BAD,

19:41.000 --> 19:42.333
AND EVEN IF IT WAS,

19:42.333 --> 19:43.667
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER
DOESN'T HURT KIDS.

19:43.667 --> 19:45.250
HE DOESN'T?

19:45.250 --> 19:47.000
DEFINITELY NOT.
YOU'RE SAFE.

19:49.458 --> 19:51.333
WHEN ARE THEY GONNA HURRY UP
AND CATCH THIS GUY?

19:51.333 --> 19:54.166
THEY ARE WORKING AS HARD
AS THEY CAN.

19:54.166 --> 19:55.875
Gail: IF WHAT I'VE HEARD
IS TRUE --

19:55.875 --> 19:57.667
THAT HE ONLY GOES
AFTER CRIMINALS --

19:57.667 --> 20:00.333
I SAY LEAVE HIM ALONE.

20:00.333 --> 20:02.500
HE'S GOT MY SEAL OF APPROVAL.

20:05.333 --> 20:09.625
PERHAPS I HAVE MISJUDGED YOU,
O WISE ONE.

20:25.625 --> 20:27.083
REALLY?

20:27.083 --> 20:29.917
YEAH, SISTER
SPILLED EVERYTHING.

20:29.917 --> 20:31.208
THINKS HE KILLED
THEIR PARENTS

20:31.208 --> 20:33.208
AND MADE IT LOOK LIKE
A CAR ACCIDENT.

20:33.208 --> 20:34.542
THE LIVING TRUST
WAS IN HIS NAME.

20:36.667 --> 20:38.709
NICE WORK.

20:38.709 --> 20:41.375
SO, WHAT'S IT GONNA BE
TONIGHT?

20:41.375 --> 20:43.667
CHINESE, ITALIAN?

20:43.667 --> 20:48.542
UH, ACTUALLY, I HAVE
A, UH, SOCIAL APPOINTMENT.

20:48.542 --> 20:49.583
[ CHUCKLES ]

20:49.583 --> 20:52.125
YOU MEAN LIKE A DATE?

20:52.125 --> 20:54.834
I GUESS YOU COULD
CALL IT THAT.

20:54.834 --> 20:57.250
WOW, LOOK AT YOU.

20:57.250 --> 21:00.291
NEW IN TOWN
AND ALREADY HOOKING UP.

21:00.291 --> 21:02.166
IT'S AN INTRODUCTION
ARRANGED BY A FRIEND.

21:02.166 --> 21:05.333
ONE NEEDS TO GET OUT AND HAVE
A LITTLE FUN ON OCCASION.

21:05.333 --> 21:08.041
IT'S SOMETHING I STRONGLY
RECOMMEND FOR YOU AS WELL.

21:08.041 --> 21:11.000
YEAH.
WITH THE HOURS WE WORK...

21:11.000 --> 21:14.000
I'M SERIOUS.
MAKE TIME FOR IT.

21:14.000 --> 21:16.250
IT'LL HELP KEEP YOU
BETTER BALANCED.

21:16.250 --> 21:18.542
YES, SIR.

21:27.041 --> 21:29.000
ARE YOU OKAY?

21:29.000 --> 21:31.875
YEAH, IT'S JUST...

21:31.875 --> 21:33.583
[ SIGHS ]

21:33.583 --> 21:35.417
...SOMETHING AT WORK.

21:36.917 --> 21:39.083
ARE YOU HANDLING IT OKAY?

21:40.291 --> 21:43.417
I ENDED UP SEEING MY SPONSOR
TODAY AT LUNCH.

21:46.333 --> 21:47.959
HOW'D THAT GO?

21:47.959 --> 21:49.667
NOT SO GREAT.

21:49.667 --> 21:52.291
SHE'S A LITTLE ODD.

21:52.291 --> 21:54.667
PLAYS A LITTLE LOOSE
WITH THE 12 STEPS.

21:54.667 --> 21:58.333
THAT DOESN'T SEEM SMART --
MAKING UP YOUR OWN.

21:58.333 --> 22:01.792
MAYBE IT'S 'CAUSE IT'S
HER FIRST TIME BEING A SPONSOR.

22:01.792 --> 22:04.208
OH.

22:04.208 --> 22:07.333
WELL, MAYBE YOU SHOULD TRY
SOMEONE ELSE.

22:08.500 --> 22:12.250
I JUST WANT TO DO WHAT'S BEST
FOR MY RECOVERY.

22:12.250 --> 22:17.834
WELL, MAYBE SOMEONE OLDER,
MORE LIKE YOU, MORE MANLY.

22:17.834 --> 22:20.625
YEAH, MAYBE.

22:20.625 --> 22:22.917
YEAH.

22:22.917 --> 22:25.500
[ UP-TEMPO MUSIC PLAYS ]

22:33.166 --> 22:35.667
♪ HEY, CONéCTENSE, ¿OKAY? ♪

22:35.667 --> 22:38.291
♪ SEGUNDA ETAPA ES IN THIS CASE
QUE HOMBRE DE LEY ♪

22:38.291 --> 22:40.083
♪ EVERY DAY ME CONCENTRO ♪

22:40.083 --> 22:42.208
♪ DENTRO DE MIS IDEAS Y PIENSO ♪

22:42.208 --> 22:45.667
♪ QUE PARA HACERLO NECESITO
ABSOLUTO SILENCIO ♪

22:45.667 --> 22:49.375
♪ UNA VEZ YA TERMINADA LA
CONCENTRACIóN, ME SIENTO... ♪

22:52.709 --> 22:54.083
HEY.

22:54.083 --> 22:55.625
HEY.

22:59.291 --> 23:00.834
YOU REMEMBER ME?

23:00.834 --> 23:02.458
YEAH.

23:02.458 --> 23:04.625
YOU'RE THE GIRL
WHO DOESN'T LIKE TAPE.

23:04.625 --> 23:06.250
DEBRA, ACTUALLY.

23:06.250 --> 23:08.000
I'M GABRIEL.

23:09.875 --> 23:11.583
DONE FOR THE NIGHT?

23:11.583 --> 23:13.208
YEAH.

23:14.959 --> 23:18.208
ANY INTEREST
IN GRABBING A DRINK?

23:21.083 --> 23:23.750
[ BOTH BREATHING HEAVILY ]

23:23.750 --> 23:26.166
USUALLY A LADY HAS TO BUY ME
DINNER FIRST.

23:26.166 --> 23:27.834
STOP TALKING
AND GET YOUR PANTS OFF.

23:30.458 --> 23:32.792
ARE YOU ALWAYS LIKE THIS?
NO.

23:32.792 --> 23:35.709
NO, I HAVEN'T EVEN HAD SEX
SINCE...

23:35.709 --> 23:37.000
SINCE WHAT?

23:38.875 --> 23:40.041
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

23:40.041 --> 23:41.250
YOU ALL RIGHT?

23:41.250 --> 23:42.500
YEAH, JUST ONE SECOND.

23:42.500 --> 23:44.166
LOOK, WE DON'T HAVE TO DO THIS,
YOU KNOW?

23:44.166 --> 23:45.667
OH.
[ LAUGHS NERVOUSLY ]

23:45.667 --> 23:50.208
OH, YOU'RE INTO
THE KINKY STUFF, HUH?

23:50.208 --> 23:52.750
NO, THE LAST GUY I HAD SEX WITH
TRIED TO KILL ME.

24:06.834 --> 24:10.709
"WHO IS
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER?"

24:10.709 --> 24:12.125
GOD.

24:12.125 --> 24:14.500
THIS OBSESSION WITH HIM
IS RELENTLESS,

24:14.500 --> 24:17.166
JUST LIKE DEB
AND THAT DAMN TREADMILL.

24:17.166 --> 24:19.291
[ SQUEAKING AND THUDDING ]

24:26.792 --> 24:29.125
DEB, DO YOU EVER STOP?

24:29.125 --> 24:31.500
DEXTER, JESUS, YOU'RE SUPPOSED
TO BE AT RITA'S!

24:31.500 --> 24:33.000
SORRY. SORRY.

24:33.000 --> 24:34.458
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

24:34.458 --> 24:36.333
[ SIGHS ]

24:36.333 --> 24:37.834
FUCK.

24:51.834 --> 24:54.041
GOOD MORNING.

24:54.041 --> 24:57.208
SO, THAT WAS A LITTLE WEIRD
LAST NIGHT.

24:57.208 --> 25:00.625
NO, YEAH.
WELL, IT WAS DARK.

25:00.625 --> 25:03.959
MY EYES HADN'T ADJUSTED.
ALL I COULD SEE WERE SHADOWS.

25:03.959 --> 25:08.834
YEAH, WELL, PLEASE PUT THOSE
SHADOWS OUT OF YOUR MIND.

25:08.834 --> 25:12.458
SO, WHAT'S THIS BIG BREAK
IN THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER CASE

25:12.458 --> 25:13.959
I KEEP HEARING ABOUT?

25:13.959 --> 25:15.083
ALGAE.

25:15.083 --> 25:16.417
ALGAE?

25:16.417 --> 25:17.542
YEAH.

25:17.542 --> 25:19.375
MASUKA FOUND
MICROSCOPIC ALGAE

25:19.375 --> 25:21.333
INSIDE THE GARBAGE BAGS
WITH THE BODIES.

25:21.333 --> 25:25.959
ALGAE UNDER THE SEA --
IMAGINE THAT.

25:25.959 --> 25:27.166
HOW DOES THAT HELP?

25:27.166 --> 25:30.792
'CAUSE THERE ARE OVER 100,000
SPECIES, ALL DIFFERENT.

25:30.792 --> 25:32.667
MASUKA THINKS HE CAN USE THEM
TO PINPOINT

25:32.667 --> 25:34.792
IN WHICH HARBOR THE KILLER
KEEPS HIS BOAT.

25:34.792 --> 25:36.417
OH.

25:36.417 --> 25:38.667
HE'S GOT SOME MARINE BIOLOGISTS
COMING DOWN TO TAKE A LOOK.

25:38.667 --> 25:40.333
CAN YOU IMAGINE
SOMETHING SO LITTLE

25:40.333 --> 25:42.000
BEING THE THING
THAT BREAKS THIS CASE?

25:42.000 --> 25:44.333
I GOT TO GO.

25:44.333 --> 25:46.333
I'LL SEE YOU AT THE STATION.

25:48.291 --> 25:50.208
IT DOESN'T MAKE SENSE.

25:50.208 --> 25:51.875
IF THERE'S ALGAE ON MY VICTIMS,

25:51.875 --> 25:55.083
IT WOULD HAVE TO COME FROM
THE OCEAN WHERE I DUMPED THEM.

25:55.083 --> 25:57.291
OBVIOUSLY,
I'M MISSING SOMETHING,

25:57.291 --> 25:58.875
AND I DON'T LIKE THAT.

26:01.291 --> 26:02.709
MRS. SOTA, I UNDERSTAND

26:02.709 --> 26:05.041
YOU WANTING TO PROTECT
YOUR HUSBAND'S REPUTATION,

26:05.041 --> 26:07.458
BUT I ALSO HAVE TO TELL YOU
THAT YOUR COOPERATION

26:07.458 --> 26:09.208
COULD HELP US CATCH
A SERIAL KILLER.

26:09.208 --> 26:10.291
I AM  COOPERATING.

26:10.291 --> 26:12.041
YOU HAVEN'T TOLD ME ANYTHING.

26:12.041 --> 26:13.166
'CAUSE THERE'S NOTHING
TO TELL!

26:18.000 --> 26:18.875
[ SIGHS ]

26:21.291 --> 26:23.208
MARIA.

26:23.208 --> 26:25.500
YOU OFF TO MEET THE MAN
FROM CURTIS' UNIT?

26:25.500 --> 26:27.250
YEAH,
AT THE BLUE WING MARINA.

26:27.250 --> 26:28.917
YOU HAVE BACKUP?

26:28.917 --> 26:30.291
OH, YEAH,
ALL KINDS OF BACKUP.

26:30.291 --> 26:31.583
HELICOPTERS AND SHIT.

26:31.583 --> 26:32.834
JAMES.

26:32.834 --> 26:35.083
LISTEN, WE GOT A MISSING
MURDER SUSPECT.

26:35.083 --> 26:38.291
THIS GUY'S A FRIEND OF HIS.
I'M JUST GONNA GO TALK TO HIM.

26:40.959 --> 26:42.959
RIGHT.

26:42.959 --> 26:45.208
YOU'RE THE LONE HOLDOUT.

26:45.208 --> 26:47.667
EVERY OTHER SUSPECT
HAS A CRIMINAL PAST,

26:47.667 --> 26:49.792
AND NOT JUST
ANY CRIMINAL PAST.

26:49.792 --> 26:51.917
THEY WERE ALL LINKED
TO MURDER.

26:51.917 --> 26:53.959
OSCAR NEVER MURDERED
ANYBODY.

26:53.959 --> 26:55.250
THEN WHY WAS HE KILLED?

26:55.250 --> 26:57.625
I DON'T KNOW. MAYBE HE FOUND OUT
WHO THE SERIAL KILLER IS!

26:57.625 --> 27:00.333
OKAY, SO YOUR HUSBAND
IS AN ENGINEER

27:00.333 --> 27:01.583
AND A SECRET CRIME FIGHTER.

27:01.583 --> 27:02.875
POR FAVOR, OLIVIA.

27:02.875 --> 27:03.792
ARE YOU THROUGH?

27:03.792 --> 27:05.458
YOU'RE GONNA TELL ME
WHAT HE DID.

27:05.458 --> 27:07.750
OH, NO.
YOU  ARE THROUGH.

27:10.500 --> 27:12.125
JUST WHAT I NEEDED.

27:34.667 --> 27:37.000
HELLO?

27:47.917 --> 27:49.291
YOU DOAKES?

27:49.291 --> 27:52.000
I AM.

27:52.000 --> 27:54.500
AND I'M GUESSING YOU'RE NOT
GONNA TELL ME YOUR NAME.

27:54.500 --> 27:56.667
I'M CURTIS BARNES.

27:59.834 --> 28:01.417
I CHECKED YOU OUT.

28:01.417 --> 28:03.291
WE KNOW A LOT
OF THE SAME PEOPLE.

28:03.291 --> 28:05.166
EVERYONE SAYS
I CAN TRUST YOU.

28:05.166 --> 28:07.750
YOU CAN TRUST ME.

28:07.750 --> 28:08.917
I JUST NEED 48 HOURS.

28:08.917 --> 28:11.000
NOW, I GOT SOMEBODY WHO'S GONNA
TAKE ME TO CUBA,

28:11.000 --> 28:13.375
BUT IT'S GONNA TAKE A DAY
TO GET THE PAPERS I NEED.

28:13.375 --> 28:14.667
SO, WHAT ARE YOU ASKING?

28:14.667 --> 28:16.625
STALL THE INVESTIGATION.

28:21.583 --> 28:23.208
LET ME ASK YOU
ONE QUESTION.

28:24.959 --> 28:25.959
YEAH.

28:28.000 --> 28:29.834
DID YOU KILL YOUR WIFE?

28:34.291 --> 28:36.875
YEAH. I KILLED ALISHA.

28:38.875 --> 28:39.750
TURN AROUND.

28:40.709 --> 28:42.500
TURN THE FUCK AROUND!

28:42.500 --> 28:43.542
NO, YOU ARE NOT
ARRESTING ME.

28:43.542 --> 28:45.125
PUT THE FUCKING GUN DOWN
AND TURN AROUND!

28:45.125 --> 28:46.000
I DON'T THINK SO.

28:57.875 --> 29:00.792
SO, HOW'D YOUR SOCIAL
APPOINTMENT GO LAST NIGHT?

29:00.792 --> 29:03.750
[ Sighing ]
OH, YOU KNOW...

29:05.667 --> 29:07.208
I TOOK YOUR ADVICE.

29:07.208 --> 29:09.542
MY ADVICE?

29:09.542 --> 29:12.208
TO GET OUT AND HAVE SOME FUN.

29:12.208 --> 29:15.083
GOT LAID BIG-TIME.

29:15.083 --> 29:16.458
OH.

29:17.834 --> 29:20.208
WELL.

29:21.959 --> 29:23.083
OH --

29:23.083 --> 29:25.875
OH, I MEAN...

29:25.875 --> 29:29.417
I DON'T USUALLY JUST GO TO
THE GYM AND PICK UP STRANGERS.

29:29.417 --> 29:32.542
THE GYM?
[ LAUGHS ]

29:32.542 --> 29:34.291
REALLY, YOU HAVE
TO SAVE ME HERE,

29:34.291 --> 29:36.583
OR I'M GONNA GO OUTSIDE
AND SHOOT MYSELF.

29:36.583 --> 29:39.250
THE WAY YOU'RE GOING,
YOU'D PROBABLY MISS.

29:39.250 --> 29:41.417
THANKS.

29:41.417 --> 29:44.792
MY DATE...WAS HORRIBLE.

29:44.792 --> 29:47.333
I PICKED HER UP, AND I DON'T
KNOW MIAMI, OF COURSE,

29:47.333 --> 29:48.709
SO I GOT US COMPLETELY LOST.

29:48.709 --> 29:51.208
AND SHE WAS CHATTERING AWAY
THE WHOLE TIME

29:51.208 --> 29:52.792
ABOUT THIS YOGI MASTER
I JUST HAVE TO MEET,

29:52.792 --> 29:54.500
SO BY THE TIME WE GOT
TO THE RESTAURANT,

29:54.500 --> 29:55.417
I WAS TEARING MY HAIR OUT.

29:55.417 --> 29:57.208
OH, GOD. I'M SORRY.

29:57.208 --> 29:58.500
NO, IT WAS GOOD.

29:58.500 --> 30:03.291
IT WAS A REMINDER THAT, UH,
I SHOULDN'T BE DATING.

30:03.291 --> 30:06.000
OF COURSE YOU SHOULD BE.

30:06.000 --> 30:08.458
NO.

30:08.458 --> 30:11.375
IT ALL COMES DOWN
TO SIMPLE MATHEMATICS.

30:11.375 --> 30:13.291
A REALLY BEAUTIFUL
RELATIONSHIP

30:13.291 --> 30:16.500
IS A ONCE-IN-A-LIFETIME
THING,

30:16.500 --> 30:18.750
AND I'VE ALREADY HAD MINE.

30:20.917 --> 30:22.667
[ TELEPHONE RINGS ]

30:22.667 --> 30:24.125
LUNDY.

30:32.834 --> 30:35.208
HEY, SO, I HEARD
YOU FOUND SOME ALGAE

30:35.208 --> 30:36.750
THAT MIGHT HELP CRACK
THE BIG CASE.

30:36.750 --> 30:38.041
YOU HEARD RIGHT.

30:38.041 --> 30:39.333
WHAT KIND OF ALGAE?

30:39.333 --> 30:40.792
DIATOMS.

30:42.917 --> 30:44.709
EUKARYOTIC ALGAE.

30:44.709 --> 30:46.542
OKAY, THIS IS THE FIRST TIME

30:46.542 --> 30:48.834
I REGRET NOT BEING
A BIGGER NERD.

30:48.834 --> 30:49.792
EUKARYOTIC?

30:49.792 --> 30:51.333
I'LL LET MANNY EXPLAIN IT
TO YOU.

30:51.333 --> 30:52.875
HE'S PICKING UP
THE EVIDENCE TOMORROW

30:52.875 --> 30:54.500
SO HE CAN STUDY IT
IN HIS OWN LAB.

30:54.500 --> 30:57.500
YOU KNOW MARINE BIOLOGISTS --
REAL PRIMA DONNAS.

30:57.500 --> 30:59.667
ANY CHANCE
YOU COULD SHOW ME?
Pascal: MASUKA.

30:59.667 --> 31:01.125
UP FRONT.

31:01.125 --> 31:02.959
OH, NO.
IT'S THAT CRAZY WITCH.

31:11.083 --> 31:12.834
WHAT IS THIS SHIT?

31:12.834 --> 31:15.041
I TOLD YOU TO FIND A SMELL.

31:15.041 --> 31:16.834
HOW FUCKING HARD
CAN THAT BE?

31:16.834 --> 31:19.792
UH, LOOK, I TOLD YOU,
A SMELL ISN'T --

31:19.792 --> 31:23.208
IT SMELLS LIKE ANOTHER WOMAN.
I CAN SMELL IT!

31:23.208 --> 31:24.625
WHY CAN'T YOU?!

31:24.625 --> 31:27.375
THIS MAN IS RUINING
MY LIFE,

31:27.375 --> 31:30.667
AND YOU ALL GO ON LIKE
NOTHING IS HAPPENING!

31:32.417 --> 31:33.875
ESMEE.

31:35.458 --> 31:36.375
COME ON, COME ON.

31:36.375 --> 31:39.375
[ CRYING ]

31:39.375 --> 31:41.000
THIS IS THE KIND OF THING

31:41.000 --> 31:43.333
THAT MAKES ME GLAD
I HAVE NO FEELINGS.

31:43.333 --> 31:44.709
LIKE THEY ALWAYS SAY,

31:44.709 --> 31:46.875
NEVER TAKE YOUR DIRTY LAUNDRY
TO WORK.

32:05.542 --> 32:07.083
WE CAN STAND HERE
ALL FUCKING DAY.

32:07.083 --> 32:09.000
I DON'T GIVE A FUCK, BUT YOU'RE
GONNA PUT THAT GUN DOWN.

32:09.000 --> 32:11.792
NOW, WE WERE BOTH RANGERS.
THAT BOND GOES DEEP.

32:11.792 --> 32:14.208
THAT DOESN'T MEAN ANYTHING
TO YOU?

32:14.208 --> 32:17.083
IF YOU WEREN'T A RANGER,
I'D HAVE SHOT YOUR ASS BY NOW.

32:19.166 --> 32:21.208
YOU KILLED YOUR WIFE, MAN.

32:25.583 --> 32:28.583
I DIDN'T MEAN TO.

32:28.583 --> 32:31.709
IT HAPPENED, MAN.

32:34.208 --> 32:35.709
YOU MARRIED?

32:35.709 --> 32:38.208
NO.

32:38.208 --> 32:40.333
EVER?

32:40.333 --> 32:42.834
ONCE.

32:42.834 --> 32:45.750
SHE DROPPED YOUR ASS,
DIDN'T SHE?

32:47.208 --> 32:48.500
WHAT --

32:48.500 --> 32:52.208
GOT TIRED OF YOU PUNCHING HOLES
IN THE WALLS,

32:52.208 --> 32:55.166
WAKING UP IN THE MIDDLE
OF THE NIGHT SCREAMING?

32:55.166 --> 33:00.959
WAS SHE ALWAYS YELLING,
"YOU GOT TO GET HELP"?

33:00.959 --> 33:03.875
SO SHE SENDS YOU
TO SOME DOCTOR,

33:03.875 --> 33:06.500
BUT YOU DON'T GO,

33:06.500 --> 33:11.542
'CAUSE YOU KNOW THERE'S NO HELP
FOR THIS KIND OF FUCKED UP.

33:11.542 --> 33:14.291
AND FINALLY,
SHE CAN'T TAKE IT ANYMORE,

33:14.291 --> 33:19.291
AND SHE JUST SAYS, "ADIóS."

33:24.667 --> 33:27.625
THAT SOUND ABOUT RIGHT?

33:29.709 --> 33:32.125
YOU GOT IT WRONG, MAN.

33:33.583 --> 33:36.333
I LEFT HER.

33:36.333 --> 33:39.834
AND WHY WAS THAT?

33:39.834 --> 33:44.458
'CAUSE I WAS AFRAID IF I DIDN'T,
I'D KILL HER.

33:49.667 --> 33:52.041
LET'S TAKE THE BOAT OUT.

33:52.041 --> 33:54.083
[ CHUCKLES ]

33:54.083 --> 33:56.166
NOW, WHY WOULD WE WANT
TO DO THAT, MAN?

33:56.166 --> 33:58.333
WE'D GET OUT OF THIS HEAT,
FOR ONE.

33:58.333 --> 34:01.959
NICE OCEAN BREEZE.

34:01.959 --> 34:04.875
MAYBE HEAD TOWARD CUBA.

34:04.875 --> 34:07.667
NO.

34:07.667 --> 34:09.583
COME ON, JUST GET ME
TO WITHIN SIGHT.

34:09.583 --> 34:10.792
I COULD SWIM FROM THERE.

34:10.792 --> 34:12.500
ONCE I'M THERE,
I COULD FIND THE --

34:12.500 --> 34:13.417
YOU'RE WASTING YOUR TIME.

34:15.125 --> 34:17.875
CURTIS, YOU'RE GOING BACK
TO THE STATION WITH ME.

34:17.875 --> 34:20.917
NO.
I'M NOT GOING TO PRISON.

34:20.917 --> 34:22.875
I DIDN'T MEAN TO KILL HER.

34:22.875 --> 34:24.834
IT'S THE ONLY WAY
OUT OF HERE.

34:28.417 --> 34:31.166
CAN'T GET YOU
TO RECONSIDER?

34:32.875 --> 34:35.667
NOT A CHANCE.

34:35.667 --> 34:38.166
WELL, THAT'S TOO BAD...

34:38.166 --> 34:42.166
'CAUSE LIKE I SAID,
I'M NOT GOING TO PRISON.

34:42.166 --> 34:44.750
PUT THE FUCKING GUN DOWN,
CURTIS.

34:44.750 --> 34:46.083
DON'T MAKE ME DO IT,
CURTIS!

34:55.250 --> 34:57.250
MOTHERFUCKER.

35:10.250 --> 35:12.917
YOU GONNA TELL ME
HOW YOU'RE DOING?

35:12.917 --> 35:15.792
I'M FINE.

35:15.792 --> 35:18.792
COME ON, DEX.
OPEN UP.

35:18.792 --> 35:21.125
VERY  FINE?

35:23.458 --> 35:25.583
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO DO BETTER
THAN THAT.

35:25.583 --> 35:29.625
WHAT'S GOING ON INSIDE
YOUR HEAD?

35:29.625 --> 35:32.333
WHAT ARE YOU THINKING?

35:33.750 --> 35:36.375
I'M AFRAID WE'RE...

35:36.375 --> 35:37.667
DONE...

35:37.667 --> 35:40.542
YOU AND I.

35:40.542 --> 35:43.709
SERIOUS?

35:43.709 --> 35:46.375
YOU'RE BREAKING UP WITH ME?

35:46.375 --> 35:51.375
ACTUALLY, I DON'T THINK I WANT
TO ANSWER ANY MORE QUESTIONS.

35:51.375 --> 35:55.333
LISTEN, DEXTER, WHATEVER YOU
THINK IS RIGHT IS WRONG.

35:55.333 --> 35:56.458
HE ASKS YOU A QUESTION,

35:56.458 --> 35:58.583
I WANT YOU TO THINK
OF YOUR ANSWER FIRST

35:58.583 --> 36:02.125
AND THEN TELL HIM
THE EXACT OPPOSITE, OKAY?

36:02.125 --> 36:04.625
Man: SO, LET'S JUST JUMP IN,
ALL RIGHT?

36:04.625 --> 36:05.625
DOES IT MAKE YOU ANGRY

36:05.625 --> 36:07.166
WHEN YOUR TEACHERS TELL YOU
WHAT TO DO?

36:08.834 --> 36:11.250
NO.

36:11.250 --> 36:13.500
ARE YOU OFTEN BORED?

36:15.542 --> 36:17.291
NO.

36:17.291 --> 36:20.125
HAVE YOU EVER KILLED
AN ANIMAL?

36:20.125 --> 36:22.667
NO. NEVER.

36:30.083 --> 36:33.250
I SHOULD GET BACK TO WORK.

36:33.250 --> 36:37.041
THANKS...
FOR EVERYTHING.

36:51.041 --> 36:54.166
I HEARD ABOUT PASCAL'S
LITTLE MELTDOWN.

36:54.166 --> 36:56.834
SHE'S BEEN UNDER A LOT
OF STRESS.

36:56.834 --> 36:58.583
YOU'RE STILL DOING IT.

36:58.583 --> 36:59.709
WHAT'S THAT?

36:59.709 --> 37:01.750
STICKING UP FOR HER.

37:01.750 --> 37:04.333
SHE IS MY SUPERIOR.

37:05.750 --> 37:09.250
YOU KNOW, I MAY HAVE
MISJUDGED YOU, MARIA.

37:09.250 --> 37:13.041
MAYBE YOU ARE MORE
THAN A POLITICAL ANIMAL.

37:13.041 --> 37:15.208
YOU JUST MIGHT BE
A REAL COP.

37:15.208 --> 37:18.792
THAT'S WHAT I'VE BEEN TRYING
TO TELL YOU.

37:18.792 --> 37:21.250
YOU'RE BACK IN CHARGE
OF HOMICIDE,

37:21.250 --> 37:23.834
EFFECTIVE IMMEDIATELY.

37:26.917 --> 37:28.500
THANK YOU.

37:30.875 --> 37:34.250
PASCAL JUST SET WOMEN IN
THE DEPARTMENT BACK 20 YEARS.

37:34.250 --> 37:36.709
IT'S UP TO YOU
TO TURN THAT AROUND.

37:46.041 --> 37:50.583
THERE IT IS,
LIKE A GIGANTIC WHITE WHALE.

37:50.583 --> 37:52.250
MY MOBY DICK.

37:57.083 --> 38:01.417
MAN, THIS HEAT.
I CAN'T TAKE IT.

38:01.417 --> 38:02.750
[ SIGHS ]

38:02.750 --> 38:07.417
I'VE GOT TO GET IN MY CAR
BEFORE I FUCKING MELT.

38:09.333 --> 38:11.667
WHICH IS EXACTLY
WHAT NEEDS TO HAPPEN

38:11.667 --> 38:14.417
TO MY DEARLY DEPARTED FRIENDS.

38:25.291 --> 38:27.959
LILA, WHAT ARE YOU
DOING HERE?

38:27.959 --> 38:29.500
HEY. DEXTER.

38:29.500 --> 38:33.875
YOU KNOW, I'VE BEEN THINKING
ABOUT YOU BREAKING UP WITH ME,

38:33.875 --> 38:38.583
AND, WELL, I DON'T THINK
IT'S IN YOUR BEST INTEREST.

38:42.333 --> 38:44.125
I'M TIRED...

38:44.125 --> 38:46.583
AND HOT,
AND I HAVE SOMEWHERE TO BE.

38:46.583 --> 38:48.750
I THINK YOU SHOULD GIVE ME
ANOTHER CHANCE.

38:48.750 --> 38:51.458
THERE'S NOTHING YOU CAN DO
TO HELP ME.

38:51.458 --> 38:53.291
IT'S NOT EVEN YOU.
IT'S ME.

38:53.291 --> 38:56.875
I AM WHO I AM,
AND NOBODY'S GONNA CHANGE THAT.

38:56.875 --> 38:59.625
WHATEVER YOU THINK YOU ARE,

38:59.625 --> 39:02.792
YOU DON'T HAVE TO BE THAT.

39:04.000 --> 39:06.041
THAT'S WHERE YOU'RE WRONG.

39:06.041 --> 39:08.875
STOP JUDGING YOURSELF.

39:08.875 --> 39:11.166
THERE ARE NO ABSOLUTES.

39:11.166 --> 39:14.458
NO ONE'S ALL GOOD OR EVIL.

39:20.000 --> 39:24.000
YOU'RE JUST GONNA HAVE
TO TRUST ME ON THIS.

39:24.000 --> 39:27.333
JESUS, DEXTER! WHAT ARE YOU
SO FUCKING SCARED OF?

39:27.333 --> 39:29.458
YOU MAKE YOURSELF
INTO A MONSTER

39:29.458 --> 39:32.333
SO YOU NO LONGER BEAR
RESPONSIBILITY FOR WHAT YOU DO.

39:32.333 --> 39:34.417
"I CAN'T HELP IT.
I'M A MONSTER.

39:34.417 --> 39:37.000
OH, OF COURSE I WAS GONNA
DO THAT -- I'M A MONSTER."

39:37.000 --> 39:40.125
IT'S SAD
AND IT'S PATHETIC...

39:40.125 --> 39:42.709
AND IT BREAKS MY HEART.

39:42.709 --> 39:45.875
YOU DON'T THINK THERE ARE
MONSTERS IN THIS WORLD?

39:45.875 --> 39:48.083
YOU DON'T BELIEVE PEOPLE
ARE EVIL?

39:53.250 --> 39:55.583
I'LL SHOW YOU EVIL.

40:11.417 --> 40:13.834
WELL, YOU WANT ME
TO OPEN ONE?

40:23.875 --> 40:26.333
[ SIGHS ]

40:26.333 --> 40:28.542
JOSEPH CEPEDA.

40:35.375 --> 40:37.542
WOW.

40:39.417 --> 40:42.041
CAN I TOUCH?

40:43.625 --> 40:45.542
OKAY.

40:51.792 --> 40:54.667
THIS ISN'T EXACTLY THE REACTION
I WAS LOOKING FOR.

40:54.667 --> 40:58.875
WELL, I'VE NEVER SEEN ANYTHING
LIKE THIS BEFORE.

40:58.875 --> 41:02.250
YOU'RE NOT DISGUSTED...

41:02.250 --> 41:04.917
APPALLED, HORRIFIED?

41:07.875 --> 41:09.875
IT'S...

41:09.875 --> 41:12.917
INCREDIBLE.

41:15.125 --> 41:17.583
BUT THE PERSON
WHO DID THIS...

41:17.583 --> 41:20.625
IS A PERSON JUST LIKE ME,

41:20.625 --> 41:22.041
LIKE YOU.

41:22.041 --> 41:25.750
WE'RE ALL GOOD, DEXTER,

41:25.750 --> 41:28.000
AND WE'RE ALL EVIL.

41:30.583 --> 41:32.417
I THOUGHT I CLOSED THE DOOR

41:32.417 --> 41:34.583
TO ANYONE EVER SEEING ME
FOR WHO I AM,

41:34.583 --> 41:36.792
BUT THIS WOMAN SEES ME.

41:36.792 --> 41:38.417
SHE DOESN'T KNOW IT,

41:38.417 --> 41:40.959
BUT SHE'S LOOKING
BEHIND THE MASK,

41:40.959 --> 41:42.250
AND SHE'S NOT TURNING AWAY.

41:44.625 --> 41:46.709
YOU REALLY IMPRESSED ME
IN THERE TODAY, SON.

41:46.709 --> 41:49.709
I DON'T KNOW HOW YOU DID IT,
BUT GREAT JOB.

41:49.709 --> 41:52.875
I JUST PRETENDED TO BE
SOMEONE ELSE.

41:52.875 --> 41:54.333
WELL, IT'S WORKING.
KEEP DOING IT.

41:54.333 --> 41:57.041
I MEAN, THAT DOCTOR DIDN'T EVEN
SEE THE MONSTER INSIDE YOU.

42:01.083 --> 42:02.625
I MEAN, NOT MONSTER.

42:02.625 --> 42:06.166
IT'S JUST, SON, YOU KNOW
THAT YOU HAVE THESE DARK URGES.

42:06.166 --> 42:08.625
ANYWAY, GOOD JOB.

42:13.750 --> 42:17.041
AND SOMEHOW,
EVEN UNDER ALL THIS PRESSURE,

42:17.041 --> 42:21.834
SHE'S ABLE TO MAKE ME FEEL OKAY
ABOUT WHO I AM AND WHAT I AM.

42:29.500 --> 42:31.750
SO...

42:33.917 --> 42:35.750
...SEE YOU SOON?

42:37.792 --> 42:39.333
YES.

42:47.041 --> 42:48.667
I'M HERE FOR YOU.

42:55.333 --> 42:57.750
[ CAR DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

42:59.208 --> 43:01.500
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

43:01.500 --> 43:03.000
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

43:20.083 --> 43:21.750
I'VE ALREADY TOLD YOU
EVERYTHING.

43:21.750 --> 43:24.333
I KNOW. I'M SORRY.

43:24.333 --> 43:27.375
I CAME HERE TO APOLOGIZE.

43:27.375 --> 43:30.083
YOU WERE VERY RUDE.

43:30.083 --> 43:31.041
I WAS.

43:32.625 --> 43:33.875
IT WAS SHAMEFUL OF ME

43:33.875 --> 43:36.417
TO DISGRACE THE MEMORY
OF YOUR HUSBAND.

43:38.750 --> 43:41.083
THANK YOU.

43:42.709 --> 43:45.625
IT'S BEEN A ROUGH FEW DAYS,

43:45.625 --> 43:50.041
NOT THAT YOU SHOULD CARE
ABOUT THAT, BUT...

43:50.041 --> 43:53.625
YOU KNOW,
ALL THESE BODIES --

43:53.625 --> 43:56.166
I'VE NEVER SEEN ANYTHING
LIKE IT.

43:56.166 --> 44:00.583
ALL MURDERED...

44:00.583 --> 44:03.709
CUT INTO PIECES.

44:03.709 --> 44:07.917
THE ONLY WAY I COULD
MAKE SENSE OUT OF IT

44:07.917 --> 44:11.417
WAS TO CONVINCE MYSELF
THAT THEY DESERVED IT.

44:11.417 --> 44:15.000
THEY ALL NEEDED
TO BE BAD PEOPLE.

44:15.000 --> 44:18.166
BUT I SHOULD NEVER HAVE
TAKEN IT OUT ON YOU.

44:28.208 --> 44:30.166
CAN YOU FEEL IT?

44:30.166 --> 44:33.208
THE BREEZE?

44:33.208 --> 44:36.542
COMING OVER THE WATER?

44:36.542 --> 44:38.792
IT'S NICE.

44:38.792 --> 44:40.458
YEAH.

44:40.458 --> 44:42.542
IT'S FINALLY COOLING DOWN.

44:49.291 --> 44:51.208
HAVE A NICE EVENING.

44:51.208 --> 44:53.959
WAIT.

44:57.709 --> 44:59.959
MY HUSBAND --

44:59.959 --> 45:03.291
HE KEPT GUNS HIDDEN
IN THE WALLS.

45:03.291 --> 45:05.333
I CAN SHOW YOU.

45:31.959 --> 45:34.875
I'VE NEVER BROKEN INTO MY OWN
PLACE OF EMPLOYMENT,

45:34.875 --> 45:36.917
BUT DESPERATE TIMES...

45:49.542 --> 45:51.834
GARBAGEMEN CAN BE SO CARELESS.

45:53.917 --> 45:57.917
Man: I SAY PUT THIS BAY HARBOR
BUTCHER ON THE CITY PAYROLL.

45:57.917 --> 46:00.083
GIVE HIM A CORNER OFFICE,
A COMPANY CAR,

46:00.083 --> 46:01.959
AND ALL THE AMMUNITION
HE NEEDS.

46:01.959 --> 46:04.959
AT LEAST SOMEBODY IS DOING
SOMETHING TO CLEAN UP MIAMI,

46:04.959 --> 46:06.583
WHICH IS MORE THAN I CAN SAY

46:06.583 --> 46:08.542
FOR THOSE FOLKS
DOWN AT CITY HALL.

46:17.250 --> 46:18.333
HEY, DEBRA.

46:18.333 --> 46:19.417
HI.

46:19.417 --> 46:22.542
SORRY ABOUT LAST NIGHT.

46:23.583 --> 46:25.750
DON'T BE.

46:25.750 --> 46:29.583
MAYBE WE CAN, UH,
DO IT AGAIN.

46:31.250 --> 46:33.583
HOW WOULD YOU FEEL
ABOUT A REAL DATE --

46:33.583 --> 46:37.125
YOU KNOW, WITH CLOTHES ON?

46:37.125 --> 46:40.125
WHERE WE ACTUALLY TALK
AND GET TO KNOW EACH OTHER?

46:40.125 --> 46:41.542
SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

46:41.542 --> 46:44.917
SOUNDS GOOD.
HOW ABOUT SATURDAY?

46:44.917 --> 46:46.792
DEAL.

46:48.417 --> 46:50.750
PICK YOU UP AT 8:00.

46:50.750 --> 46:52.500
[ LAUGHS ]

46:56.333 --> 46:57.792
AND WITH US RIGHT NOW,

46:57.792 --> 46:59.125
WE HAVE PSYCHOLOGIST
SANDY RAMOS

46:59.125 --> 47:01.959
TO PROVIDE INSIGHT INTO
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER --

47:01.959 --> 47:05.792
EVIL SERIAL KILLER
OR AVENGING FORCE FOR GOOD?

47:08.667 --> 47:12.000
THIS IS THE LAST TIME.

47:12.000 --> 47:14.000
BERTRAND?

47:14.000 --> 47:15.125
[ SIGHS ]

47:15.125 --> 47:17.917
BABE, COME ON.
YOU DON'T MEAN THAT.

47:17.917 --> 47:20.375
NO, I DO MEAN IT.
I DO.

47:20.375 --> 47:21.750
I CAN'T SEE YOU ANYMORE.

47:21.750 --> 47:24.709
WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, WAIT, NO.
NO, WAIT, NO.

47:24.709 --> 47:27.208
I DON'T UNDERSTAND, MARIA.

47:27.208 --> 47:29.709
THIS -- THIS IS DONE.

47:29.709 --> 47:31.792
SHE'S GONE.
IT'S OVER WITH.

47:31.792 --> 47:36.375
WE CAN FINALLY BE OUT
IN THE OPEN.

47:36.375 --> 47:38.959
JUST YOU AND ME, OKAY?

47:38.959 --> 47:41.875
Just like what we wanted.

47:41.875 --> 47:44.667
NO, BERTRAND, STOP.

47:44.667 --> 47:48.291
STOP IT.
STOP, STOP, STOP. STOP!

47:50.333 --> 47:53.333
[ SIGHS ]
GO BACK TO ESMEE.

47:56.709 --> 47:58.667
SO, WHAT,
THIS IS HOW IT IS?

48:00.875 --> 48:02.709
YOU GET YOUR JOB BACK,

48:02.709 --> 48:05.625
AND NOW YOU -- YOU'RE --
YOU'RE THROUGH WITH ME?

48:05.625 --> 48:06.834
LOOK, DON'T PLAY THE VICTIM.

48:06.834 --> 48:09.041
YOU KNEW WHAT THIS WAS
FROM THE BEGINNING.

48:09.041 --> 48:11.500
[ SCOFFS ]

48:11.500 --> 48:15.083
YOU ARE ONE COLDHEARTED BITCH,
I'LL TELL YOU THAT.

48:16.625 --> 48:19.000
NO, YOU DON'T GET
TO TELL ME ANYTHING!

48:19.000 --> 48:22.166
I AM NOT THE PIECE OF SHIT
FUCKING ANOTHER WOMAN

48:22.166 --> 48:23.375
BEHIND HIS FIANCéE'S BACK!

48:23.375 --> 48:25.667
YOU TRY AND JUDGE ME,
ASSHOLE.

48:28.625 --> 48:31.083
YOU DON'T KNOW
THE FIRST THING ABOUT ME.

48:43.709 --> 48:46.667
YEAH, SO,
I THINK I MISJUDGED LILA.

48:46.667 --> 48:49.333
ARE YOU SURE?

48:49.333 --> 48:50.709
I MEAN,
SHE'S UNCONVENTIONAL,

48:50.709 --> 48:54.208
BUT I THINK SHE'S THE BEST
SPONSOR...FOR ME.

48:56.375 --> 48:59.208
WELL, IF SHE CAN HELP
KEEP YOU CLEAN.

48:59.208 --> 49:01.083
CHOP, CHOP, CHOP, CHOP,
CHOP, CHOP, CHOP, CHOP!

49:01.083 --> 49:04.625
WHOA, WHO'S THIS?
COULD IT BE ROBIN HOOD?

49:04.625 --> 49:06.834
NO, I'M THE BUTCHER MAN!

49:06.834 --> 49:08.041
I MADE IT FOR HIM.

49:08.041 --> 49:10.959
I THOUGHT IT MIGHT HELP
WITH THE NIGHTMARES.

49:10.959 --> 49:13.166
BET YOU DIDN'T KNOW
YOU COULD FLY.

49:13.166 --> 49:16.250
[ LAUGHING ]

49:19.667 --> 49:25.166
Dexter: HAVE I MISJUDGED LILA?
I HAVE NO IDEA.

49:25.166 --> 49:28.333
I DO KNOW SHE'S HELPING ME LOOK
AT MYSELF IN A DIFFERENT WAY.

49:30.917 --> 49:32.750
HE'S GOOD, THAT ONE.

49:32.750 --> 49:35.500
I KNOW.
I GOT LUCKY.

49:35.500 --> 49:38.959
QUITE AN ACTOR.

49:38.959 --> 49:42.083
HE'S HIDING SOMETHING.
I'M SURE OF IT.

49:45.542 --> 49:48.250
[ LAUGHING ]

49:51.458 --> 49:53.959
FOR EXAMPLE,
WE FIND THE GENUS NITZSCHIA,

49:53.959 --> 49:56.834
AND WE KNOW WE'RE TALKING
ABOUT A FRESHWATER MARINA,

49:56.834 --> 49:58.625
AND THE ALGAE
CAN TELL US MORE

49:58.625 --> 50:00.959
ABOUT WHAT KIND OF POLLUTANTS
ARE IN THE WATER,

50:00.959 --> 50:03.458
WHICH WOULD EVEN FURTHER
NARROW...

50:05.333 --> 50:07.250
[ RETCHES ]

50:07.250 --> 50:08.792
[ VOMITING ]

50:21.375 --> 50:22.959
DAMN IT!

50:24.834 --> 50:26.291
FOR THE FIRST TIME,

50:26.291 --> 50:30.417
I FEEL THE FUTURE MIGHT HOLD
SOMETHING DIFFERENT FOR ME.

50:30.417 --> 50:33.583
IT'S POSSIBLE
I'M JUST FOOLING MYSELF,

50:33.583 --> 50:35.875
BUT I'M WILLING
TO TAKE THE RISK.

50:38.125 --> 50:40.125
FUCKING GARBAGEMEN.

50:40.125 --> 50:41.083
OH?

50:41.083 --> 50:42.709
BROKE THE
REFRIGERATION UNIT.

50:42.709 --> 50:44.166
IT BLEW HOT AIR ALL NIGHT.

50:44.166 --> 50:47.166
IT TURNED THE BODIES
INTO PINK MUSH.

50:47.166 --> 50:49.542
HOW AWFUL!

50:49.542 --> 50:50.750
COMPLETELY RUINED.

50:50.750 --> 50:52.875
[ SIGHS ]

50:52.875 --> 50:56.166
YOU BROUGHT YOUR MARINE
BIOLOGIST AND EVERYTHING.

50:56.166 --> 50:59.333
YEAH.
IT MADE HIM VOMIT.

51:00.375 --> 51:03.125
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

51:03.125 --> 51:05.917
ANYWAY, GOOD THING THE HEAT
DIDN'T AFFECT THE ROCKS.

51:05.917 --> 51:09.041
LUNDY HAD US STORE THEM
SEPARATELY.

51:09.041 --> 51:10.750
THE ROCKS?

51:10.750 --> 51:13.041
YEAH. THE ALGAE WE FOUND
ON THE ROCKS.

51:13.041 --> 51:16.166
THE BAY HARBOR BUTCHER USED THEM
TO WEIGH HIS BAGS DOWN.

51:16.166 --> 51:19.208
WE'RE ASSUMING HE PICKED THEM UP
WHERE HE DOCKS HIS BOAT.

51:23.208 --> 51:25.542
BUT I THOUGHT
THE MARINE BIOLOGIST

51:25.542 --> 51:27.000
CAME TO EXAMINE THE BODIES.

51:27.000 --> 51:29.709
NO. NO, IT'S ALL ABOUT
THE ROCKS, BABY.

51:29.709 --> 51:30.959
MANNY TOOK HIM TO HIS LAB.

51:30.959 --> 51:32.500
SHOULD HAVE RESULTS
IN A WEEK OR SO.

51:32.500 --> 51:36.750
THAT SHOULD HELP US NARROW DOWN
WHAT MARINA THEY CAME FROM.

51:36.750 --> 51:39.375
IT'S AN ODD SENSATION
TO BE EXPERIENCING

51:39.375 --> 51:42.583
WHAT MIGHT BE CALLED HOPE
FOR THE FIRST TIME IN MY LIFE.

51:42.583 --> 51:44.166
AT THE SAME TIME,

51:44.166 --> 51:46.083
I SUDDENLY FIND MYSELF
WEIGHING THE BENEFITS

51:46.083 --> 51:49.458
OF ELECTROCUTION
VERSUS LETHAL INJECTION.

51:49.458 --> 51:51.083
BUT HERE I AM.
